    {
      "id": "batchjob_text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -645.3333333333335,
      "y": 27,
      "width": 184,
      "height": 195,
      "text": "Batch Job\n(Single Job)\n\n\u2460 Count AVAILABLE\n   If \u2265 HIGH_WATERMARK (%)\n   \u2192 exit, do nothing\n\n\u2461 Prefetch delta tokens\n   (HIGH_WATERMARK (%) - count)\n\n\u23f0 Cron: every ~1hr\n\ud83d\udcc9 Also: threshold trigger",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeColor": "#1864ab",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "version": 86,
