      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Batch Job\n(Single Job)\n\n\u2460 Count AVAILABLE\n   If \u2265 HIGH_WATERMARK (%)\n   \u2192 exit, do nothing\n\n\u2461 Prefetch delta tokens\n   (HIGH_WATERMARK (%) - count)\n\n\u23f0 Cron: every ~1hr\n\ud83d\udcc9 Also: threshold trigger",
